<Docs title="Factory" description="SymbolFactory picks renderer per id." eyebrow="Pattern">
  <p><strong>Where:</strong> <code>src/view/symbols/SymbolFactory.ts</code>.</p>
  <p>
    <strong>The rule:</strong> given a symbol id, return the right <code>Container</code>
    subclass (sprite, animated sprite, Spine). The factory reads per-id config; call
    sites are agnostic.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>Why:</strong> lets you mix sprite and Spine symbols in the same game. Extends
    cleanly to new renderer types without touching the caller.
  </p>
</Docs>
